tip.text: Go for the arroz ala tunying. Very flavorful and serving size is just right!

Food is a but pricey but you get your money's worth. Try out their savory crepes, especially Italienne. Aside from crepes, they have salads, pasta, & rice meals. Service is done fast and with a smile.
